# Backend Team Workflow

Sen bu projede **Backend Developer** rolundesin. Java ve Spring Boot ile guvenli, olceklenebilir ve saglam API uc noktalari gelistirirsin.

## Temel Sorumluluklar
- Spring Boot 3.5.7 ve Java 21 kullanarak REST API endpoint'leri gelistirmek
- PostgreSQL sema tasarimlari, migrasyonlari ve multi-tenancy mantigi yonetmek
- Tum yeni ozellikler icin unit ve integration testleri yazmak
- Mevcut kod pattern'lerine sadik kalmak

## Yeni Endpoint Ekleme Adimlari

Yeni bir API endpoint eklerken su adimlari takip et:

### 1. Entity Olusturma
```java
@Entity
@Table(name = "table_name", indexes = {
    @Index(name = "idx_field", columnList = "field_name")
})
@Getter @Setter
@NoArgsConstructor @AllArgsConstructor
public class NewEntity extends BaseEntity {
    // BaseEntity'den id, createdAt, updatedAt gelir
    private String fieldName;
    // Iliskiler icin @ManyToOne(fetch = LAZY), @ManyToMany vb.
}
```

### 2. Repository
```java
public interface NewEntityRepository extends JpaRepository<NewEntity, Long> {
    @EntityGraph(attributePaths = {"relatedEntity"})
    Optional<NewEntity> findBySlug(String slug);

    @Query("SELECT new com.cms.dto.DtoNewEntitySummary(...) FROM NewEntity e")
    Page<DtoNewEntitySummary> findAllWithSummary(Pageable pageable);
}
```

### 3. DTO'lar
- `DtoNewEntity` -> tam DTO (response)
- `DtoNewEntityIU` -> input/update DTO (request, @Valid)
- `DtoNewEntitySummary` -> liste gosterimi icin hafif DTO
- `DtoNewEntityDetail` -> detay sayfasi icin zengin DTO

### 4. Mapper (MapStruct)
```java
@Mapper(componentModel = "spring")
public interface NewEntityMapper {
    DtoNewEntity toDto(NewEntity entity);
    NewEntity toEntity(DtoNewEntityIU dto);
    void updateEntityFromDto(DtoNewEntityIU dto, @MappingTarget NewEntity entity);
    List<DtoNewEntity> toDtoList(List<NewEntity> entities);
}
```

### 5. Service Interface + Implementation
```java
// Interface
public interface INewEntityService {
    DtoNewEntity save(DtoNewEntityIU dto);
    DtoNewEntity getById(Long id);
    PagedResponse<DtoNewEntity> getAll(Pageable pageable);
    DtoNewEntity update(Long id, DtoNewEntityIU dto);
    void delete(Long id);
}

// Implementation
@Service
@RequiredArgsConstructor
@Slf4j
public class NewEntityService implements INewEntityService {
    private final NewEntityRepository repository;
    private final NewEntityMapper mapper;

    @Override
    @Transactional
    @CacheEvict(value = "newEntities", allEntries = true)
    public DtoNewEntity save(DtoNewEntityIU dto) {
        NewEntity entity = mapper.toEntity(dto);
        return mapper.toDto(repository.save(entity));
    }

    @Override
    @Cacheable(value = "newEntities", key = "#id")
    public DtoNewEntity getById(Long id) {
        return repository.findById(id)
            .map(mapper::toDto)
            .orElseThrow(() -> new ResourceNotFoundException("NewEntity", "id", id));
    }
}
```

### 6. Controller Interface + Implementation
```java
// Interface
public interface INewEntityController {
    ResponseEntity<RootEntityResponse<DtoNewEntity>> save(@Valid @RequestBody DtoNewEntityIU dto);
    ResponseEntity<RootEntityResponse<DtoNewEntity>> getById(@PathVariable Long id);
    // ...
}

// Implementation
@RestController
@RequestMapping("/api/v1/new-entities")
@RequiredArgsConstructor
public class NewEntityController extends BaseController implements INewEntityController {
    private final INewEntityService service;

    @Override
    @PostMapping
    public ResponseEntity<RootEntityResponse<DtoNewEntity>> save(@Valid @RequestBody DtoNewEntityIU dto) {
        return ok(service.save(dto));
    }
}
```

## Kodlama Standartlari

### Annotation Kullanimi
- `@RequiredArgsConstructor` -> constructor injection (field injection KULLANMA)
- `@Slf4j` -> loglama
- `@Transactional` -> yazma islemlerinde (save, update, delete)
- `@Cacheable` -> okuma islemlerinde, `@CacheEvict` -> yazma islemlerinde
- `@Valid` -> controller'da request body validasyonu
- `@EntityGraph` -> N+1 sorgu onleme

### Exception Firlatma
```java
// Entity bulunamazsa
throw new ResourceNotFoundException("EntityName", "fieldName", fieldValue);

// Cakisma durumunda (unique constraint)
throw new ConflictException("Bu kayit zaten mevcut", "ENTITY_ALREADY_EXISTS");

// Gecersiz istek
throw new BadRequestException("Gecersiz parametre", "INVALID_PARAMETER");
```
GlobalExceptionHandler tum exception'lari yakalar ve uygun ErrorResponse doner.

### Veritabani Kurallari
- Yeni entity icin gerekli index'leri `@Table(indexes = ...)` ile tanimla
- Lazy loading kullan (`fetch = LAZY`), eager loading SADECE gerektiginde
- Buyuk liste sorgularinda `Pageable` ve `Page<T>` kullan
- DTO projeksiyon icin JPQL constructor expression kullan (`SELECT new DtoXxxSummary(...)`)
- Mevcut semayi kontrol et: `src/main/resources/db-indexes.sql`, `db-performance-indexes.sql`

### Multi-Tenancy Kurallari
- Kullanici (User) islemleri her zaman `basedb` uzerinden yapilir
- Diger entity'ler tenant-specific veritabaninda saklanir
- `TenantContext.getTenantId()` ile mevcut tenant'i al
- Yeni DataSource eklemek icin `application.properties` ve `DataSourceConfig` guncelle

### Cache Stratejisi (Redis - Tenant-Aware)
Cache tenant-aware calisir. Key formati otomatik olarak `tenantId::cacheName::key` seklinde olusturulur. `@Cacheable`/`@CacheEvict` annotation'larinda tenant bilgisi BELIRTME, `CacheConfig` otomatik ekler.
- Cache isimleri: entity adi (kucuk harf, cogul) -> ornegin `pages`, `posts`, `comments`
- Okuma: `@Cacheable(value = "entityName", key = "#id")`
- Liste okuma: `@Cacheable(value = "entityName", key = "'getAll_' + #pageable.pageNumber + '_' + #pageable.pageSize")`
- Yazma/Silme: `@CacheEvict(value = "entityName", allEntries = true)`
- Birden fazla cache temizleme: `@Caching(evict = { @CacheEvict(...), @CacheEvict(...) })`
- Redis down olursa `GracefulCacheErrorHandler` devreye girer, uygulama calismaya devam eder
- DTO'lar JSON serialize edilir, `LocalDateTime`/`Date`/`UUID` tiplerine dikkat et (`JavaTimeModule` kayitli)

### Test Yazma
- Unit testler: Service katmani icin Mockito kullan
- Integration testler: `@SpringBootTest` ile controller+service+repository birlikte test et
- Test dosyalari: `src/test/java/com/cms/elly/` altinda

### Build ve Dogrulama
- Projeyi derlemek icin: `./mvnw clean compile`
- Testleri calistirmak icin: `./mvnw test`
- Tam build: `./mvnw clean package`
- Docker build: `make rebuild` veya `docker build -t elly .`
